Samsung Electronics Co., Ltd. is a South Korean multinational major appliance and consumer electronics corporation headquartered in Yeongtong-gu, Suwon, South Korea.
<br>Samsung has been the world's largest manufacturer of mobile phones and smartphones since 2011,and is best known for its Samsung Galaxy brand.
<br>It is currently the pinnacle of the Samsung chaebol, accounting for 70% of the group's revenue in 2012.